{"tid":1673214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Mon post嘅狗狗入一入，好執定包袱","createTime":"2019-10-24T13:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T14:22:00.000Z","uid":59511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"247519c9a0e21816980b03fb6f873a4f7f48f581","tid":1673214,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"呢場運動贏唔贏到我唔知，但我知你哋做狗嘅就一定輸。<br />\n情況一：<br />\n示威者贏，你班狗狗肯定被清算就唔多講<br />\n<br />\n情況二：<br />\n示威者同政府deal到，市面回復平靜。市民對狗隊接近零信任（你可以睇下民調），要有效管治，冇接任者會揹咁大舊負資產，一啲中低級嘅狗狗隨時為左政治被生祭以換取對政府嘅信心，自己睇路<br />\n<br />\n情況三：<br />\n政府勝，兔死狗烹。你班狗成日以下犯上妄議朝政，你幾時聽過武警/老解公開話京官做得唔岩，黨嘅方針一定係黨指揮槍我係京官洗撚留你。到時狗隊有一輪大清洗係必然嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n場運動完嘅時候就到你地狗狗受靶之時。仲睇？係我就執定包袱著草/轉行。"},{"pid":"0a5f4f3965202cc01a6a76f0632a58ddd4c4910d","tid":1673214,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sw3aYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Sw3aYY.jpg&h=18631120&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8f08b2ac756b37bf3a08ec6188bf2a476afdce12","tid":1673214,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:54:46.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會識，亦冇腦理解"},{"pid":"f48540ae74b0bac650e957419232a6d93a699620","tid":1673214,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"阿sir唔使驚，睇我呢個post有方法拆解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警</strong>犯咗死罪</span>，已<span style=\"color: red;\">大禍臨頭</span>！<br />\n+ <span style=\"color: gold;\">送條妙計<strong>俾科士解圍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671833</a>"},{"pid":"3fceb8140ec92ee0d50e52bdbb76c477013034bf","tid":1673214,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><st